'''Unlos Tagge''' was the capital city of [[Tepasi/Legends|Tepasi]]. It was believed to have been named after the founding member of the [[House of Tagge/Legends|House of Tagge]], himself one of the Founding Fathers of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]].

